---
layout: layouts/base.njk
pagination:
  data: langs.codes
  size: 1
  alias: lang
eleventyComputed:
  permalink: "{{ 'about' | permalinkFor(lang) }}index.html"
  title: "{{ meta[lang].about.title }}"
  description: "{{ meta[lang].about.description }}"
  pageKey: 'about'
---
{% set d = dict[lang] %}
  <main id="main">
    <!-- PAGE HERO -->
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="page-hero__bg" aria-hidden="true">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1582719478250-c89cae4dc85b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1920&q=80" alt="" loading="eager" />
      </div>
      <div class="container page-hero__content">
        <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--light" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-5)"><span class="eyebrow__dot"></span>About Us</span>
        <h1>People who treat cleaning as a craft.</h1>
        <p>We're a small studio with big standards. Every clean is a chance to earn your trust — one detail at a time.</p>
        <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
          <a href="{{ 'home' | url(lang) }}"><span>{{ 'nav.home' | t(d) }}</span></a>
          <span class="breadcrumb__sep">/</span>
          <span>About</span>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- MISSION & VISION -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
          <span class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow__dot"></span>What Drives Us</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">Our mission & vision</h2>
          <p class="section-subtitle">Two short sentences that shape every decision we make.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mv-grid" data-stagger="180">
          <article class="mv-card">
            <div class="mv-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polygon points="16.24 7.76 14.12 14.12 7.76 16.24 9.88 9.88 16.24 7.76"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Our Mission</h3>
            <p>To elevate the standard of cleaning in every home and business we touch — proving that a spotless space is not a luxury, but a foundation for clearer thinking, calmer living, and more productive work. We exist to give people their time back, and a space they're proud of.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="mv-card">
            <div class="mv-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Our Vision</h3>
            <p>To become the Rhein-Ruhr-Region's most quietly trusted cleaning studio — known not for marketing volume, but for the calibre of our crews, the rigour of our training, and the relationships we build with each client. We will never franchise. We will never compromise on the people who do the work.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- VALUES -->
    <section class="section section--tinted">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
          <span class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow__dot"></span>What We Stand For</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">Five values, lived daily</h2>
          <p class="section-subtitle">These aren't posters on a wall. They're the filters we run every decision through.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="values-grid" data-stagger="120">
          <article class="value-card">
            <div class="value-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h4>Integrity</h4>
            <p>We do what we said we'd do, exactly when we said we'd do it. If we mess up, we say so — and we fix it, fast, no excuses.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="value-card">
            <div class="value-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h4>Craft</h4>
            <p>Cleaning is not a chore to us — it's a craft. We study tools, techniques, and chemistry so you don't have to think about any of it.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="value-card">
            <div class="value-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h4>Care</h4>
            <p>We treat every space as if it were our own. Your home, your office, your restaurant — it matters to us because it matters to you.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="value-card">
            <div class="value-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h4>Reliability</h4>
            <p>You'll never have to wonder if we're showing up. Same crew, same time, same spotless result — visit after visit, year after year.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="value-card">
            <div class="value-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2v4m0 12v4m10-10h-4M6 12H2m15.07-7.07-2.83 2.83M9.76 14.24l-2.83 2.83m0-10 2.83 2.83m4.48 4.48 2.83 2.83"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h4>Sustainability</h4>
            <p>Plant-based products, refillable bottles, electric vehicles. We obsess over our environmental footprint as much as your dust bunnies.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="value-card">
            <div class="value-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h4>People First</h4>
            <p>Our crews are employees, not contractors. They earn a living wage, get healthcare, and stay with us for years. You meet the same faces.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TIMELINE -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
          <span class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow__dot"></span>Our Journey</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">Fifteen years, one obsession</h2>
          <p class="section-subtitle">From a single Düsseldorfer Wohnung to the Rhein-Ruhr-Region's most quietly trusted cleaning studio.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="max-width: 760px; margin-inline: auto;" data-reveal>
          <div class="timeline">
            <div class="timeline-item">
              <div class="timeline-item__dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
              <span class="timeline-item__year">2010</span>
              <h4 class="timeline-item__title">The first apartment</h4>
              <p class="timeline-item__desc">Founder Amélie Laurent starts BlitzBlank in a 400 sq ft Düsseldorfer Altstadt-Studio, cleaning for neighbours on weekends with a borrowed vacuum and a single bucket of plant-based products.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
              <div class="timeline-item__dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
              <span class="timeline-item__year">2013</span>
              <h4 class="timeline-item__title">First commercial client</h4>
              <p class="timeline-item__desc">Northwind Studio signs on as our first recurring office contract — and is still a client today. We hire our first three full-time crew members.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
              <div class="timeline-item__dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
              <span class="timeline-item__year">2016</span>
              <h4 class="timeline-item__title">The Königsallee-Zentrale</h4>
              <p class="timeline-item__desc">We move into a converted warehouse on Königsallee, build a formal training program, and adopt our 80-hour onboarding curriculum for every new hire.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
              <div class="timeline-item__dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
              <span class="timeline-item__year">2019</span>
              <h4 class="timeline-item__title">Medical & industrial divisions</h4>
              <p class="timeline-item__desc">Specialised crews trained to OSHA, HIPAA, and CDC standards launch. We pass every audit on first inspection — a streak we still hold today.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
              <div class="timeline-item__dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
              <span class="timeline-item__year">2022</span>
              <h4 class="timeline-item__title">All-electric fleet</h4>
              <p class="timeline-item__desc">The last combustion van retires. Every vehicle in our fleet is electric. Carbon-neutral certification achieved through combination of EVs, solar-powered HQ, and verified offsets.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
              <div class="timeline-item__dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
              <span class="timeline-item__year">2025</span>
              <h4 class="timeline-item__title">500 clients & counting</h4>
              <p class="timeline-item__desc">A milestone we celebrated quietly with a team dinner. Same mission, same standards, same refusal to franchise. The next decade starts tomorrow.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TEAM -->
    <section class="section section--tinted">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
          <span class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow__dot"></span>The People</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">Meet the leadership team</h2>
          <p class="section-subtitle">The hands-on crew behind every spotless space. You'll see them on site — not behind a desk.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="services-grid" data-stagger="120" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));">
          <article class="team-card">
            <img class="team-card__photo" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573497019940-1c28c88b4f3e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" alt="Portrait of Amélie Laurent, Founder & CEO" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="team-card__body">
              <h4 class="team-card__name">Amélie Laurent</h4>
              <span class="team-card__role">Founder & CEO</span>
              <div class="team-card__socials">
                <a href="#" aria-label="Amélie on LinkedIn"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-4 0v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"/><rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="12"/><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"/></svg></a>
                <a href="#" aria-label="Amélie on Twitter"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M18.244 2H21.5l-7.5 8.572L22.5 22h-6.928l-5.42-7.09L3.8 22H.543l8.022-9.17L1 2h7.1l4.9 6.49L18.244 2z"/></svg></a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="team-card">
            <img class="team-card__photo" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" alt="Portrait of Marcus Bell, Operations Director" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="team-card__body">
              <h4 class="team-card__name">Marcus Bell</h4>
              <span class="team-card__role">Operations Director</span>
              <div class="team-card__socials">
                <a href="#" aria-label="Marcus on LinkedIn"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-4 0v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"/><rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="12"/><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"/></svg></a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="team-card">
            <img class="team-card__photo" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580489944761-15a19d654956?auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" alt="Portrait of Priya Sharma, Training Lead" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="team-card__body">
              <h4 class="team-card__name">Priya Sharma</h4>
              <span class="team-card__role">Training Lead</span>
              <div class="team-card__socials">
                <a href="#" aria-label="Priya on LinkedIn"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-4 0v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"/><rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="12"/><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"/></svg></a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="team-card">
            <img class="team-card__photo" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472099645785-5658abf4ff4e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" alt="Portrait of Daniel Cho, Commercial Lead" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="team-card__body">
              <h4 class="team-card__name">Daniel Cho</h4>
              <span class="team-card__role">Commercial Lead</span>
              <div class="team-card__socials">
                <a href="#" aria-label="Daniel on LinkedIn"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-4 0v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"/><rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="12"/><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"/></svg></a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CERTIFICATES -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
          <span class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow__dot"></span>Credentials</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">Certified, insured, audited</h2>
          <p class="section-subtitle">The boring paperwork that lets you sleep at night. We've done all of it.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="services-grid" data-stagger="100" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));">
          <article class="cert-card">
            <div class="cert-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="cert-card__title">Fully Insured</div>
            <div class="cert-card__sub">$2M general liability</div>
          </article>
          <article class="cert-card">
            <div class="cert-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/><path d="M21 12c0 4.97-4.03 9-9 9s-9-4.03-9-9 4.03-9 9-9 9 4.03 9 9z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="cert-card__title">Bonded</div>
            <div class="cert-card__sub">Fidelity bonded crew</div>
          </article>
          <article class="cert-card">
            <div class="cert-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="cert-card__title">EPA Safer Choice</div>
            <div class="cert-card__sub">All products certified</div>
          </article>
          <article class="cert-card">
            <div class="cert-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M8 12h8M12 8v8"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="cert-card__title">OSHA Compliant</div>
            <div class="cert-card__sub">Industrial & medical</div>
          </article>
          <article class="cert-card">
            <div class="cert-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="cert-card__title">Carbon Neutral</div>
            <div class="cert-card__sub">Verified since 2022</div>
          </article>
          <article class="cert-card">
            <div class="cert-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="cert-card__title">BBB A+ Rated</div>
            <div class="cert-card__sub">Accredited business</div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- EXPERIENCE / STATS -->
    <section class="section section--dark">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
          <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--light"><span class="eyebrow__dot"></span>By the Numbers</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">Fifteen years, told in figures</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="stats-grid" data-stagger="120">
          <div class="stat-card">
            <span class="stat-card__num"><span data-counter="15" data-suffix="+">0</span></span>
            <span class="stat-card__label">Years in Business</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <span class="stat-card__num"><span data-counter="42">0</span></span>
            <span class="stat-card__label">Crew Members</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <span class="stat-card__num"><span data-counter="12500" data-suffix="+">0</span></span>
            <span class="stat-card__label">Cleans Completed</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <span class="stat-card__num"><span data-counter="98" data-suffix="%">0</span></span>
            <span class="stat-card__label">Client Retention</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="promo-banner" data-reveal>
          <div class="promo-banner__content">
            <h2>Ready to meet your crew?</h2>
            <p>Book a free walkthrough and we'll introduce you to the team, walk your space, and craft a cleaning plan that fits your life — no pressure, no obligation.</p>
            <div class="hero__cta" style="justify-content: center; opacity:1; animation: none;">
              <a href="{{ 'contact' | url(lang) }}" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg" data-magnetic>Book your walkthrough</a>
              <a href="{{ 'services' | url(lang) }}" class="btn btn--ghost-light btn--lg">Browse services</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
